{"tid":1901311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"伊朗副總統感染新型肺炎　禁止中國公民入境","createTime":"2020-02-27T17:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T18:00:48.000Z","uid":125193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea4d3f3e5656cfd0f0b26b94f02164fd40f571a","tid":1901311,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"伊朗國營通訊社報道，由於新型肺炎疫情持續，政府已禁止中國公民入境。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗新增過百宗病例，累計超過240宗，死亡人數增至26人，其中一名新增患者，是伊朗國會國家安全和外交委員會主席宗努爾，現時已被隔離，他來自重災區聖城庫姆，當地共有63宗病例。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗傳媒報道，伊朗副總統埃卜特卡爾亦確診感染。衛生部門預料，未來幾天病例會大幅增加。伊朗鄰近多國都有確診病例，其中伊拉克首都巴格達亦確診首宗病例，該名患者到過伊朗，全國累計6宗病例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511315-20200227.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511315-20200227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=52a06c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511315-20200227.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=74cbecf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511315-20200227.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2e1749a1f48939a30f7b8cc9427266397ab0b401","tid":1901311,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"嚟緊九月就立法會選舉啦<br />\n五月頭就會截止登記<br />\n無論你係地區直選定係功能組別<br />\n各位手足都快啲登記做選民啦<br />\n特別係啱啱足夠18歲嘅各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係最低成本為香港出一分力嘅方法啊<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Feform%2FREO-1%28C&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0T2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=b54b12bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C</a>)_eSign.pdf<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲填左上面呢份表格之後寄返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458ffe7bb35d090cc8f1d0d15c701fac9c12bb04","tid":1901311,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5f5a2a42281835b3067f93d89d62a9b508b927","tid":1901311,"uid":49938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"副總統都奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c20576bb9be208a0c0a86a219b4e68895913753","tid":1901311,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"伊朗出事了<br />\n成個內閣一獲熟"},{"pid":"28726b61ee2033dae8cea7a2f5343fe226ded485","tid":1901311,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"[其實對家唔係戇鳩] 黃圈被滲透及分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ba97250d118d756a5cf60e202b6ba9b573c9fe5","tid":1901311,"uid":305518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T18:00:48.000Z","msg":"軸心國自爆"}]}